{"tid":644144,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有責任感既人，返工真係好蝕底","createTime":"2018-04-27T04:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T10:52:03.000Z","uid":49643,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7746ad85ef5b6136a91b74596ea3b8e64af671","tid":644144,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"自問都算係一個有責任感既人，係公司做野雖然未必係最好，但起碼做好本份，之後就仆街，個個有問題都第一個搵自己，明明有其他同事都做同一個職位，更加資深既唔搵，都係要搵我，搞到日日自己都好似好多野做咁，有咩辦法可以改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccb7e72840c6372c09261aa7c04696fe2dc913e","tid":644144,"uid":156144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"做比意見嘅人 唔係落手落腳幫佢做埋"},{"pid":"43395e237c919b44b98606a57735b1980cb0323a","tid":644144,"uid":76632,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"職場三寶<br />\n<br />\n唔知，唔識，唔理。"},{"pid":"41b1943f4e4a8dba6ec3ee583bb5ba8981121fe2","tid":644144,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n但我本身都係無乜責任感<br />\n太忙會hea做<br />\n佢地就覺得我做得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又做錯，佢地又改完彈返黎<br />\n但一樣會覺得我好做到野。痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2584412ca6a238a5655642903a66fa01101562e9","tid":644144,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"有時冇人搵自己，會諗係咪自己太廢，問其他人都唔問自己<br />\n到有人搵又會心諗&quot;咪撚咩狗屎垃圾都搵我啦，明明有手有腳都識做既野,搵新人都得啦&quot;"},{"pid":"4612f707fb80db50d355e98423ada5bf7231b699","tid":644144,"uid":34949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43395e237c919b44b98606a57735b1980cb0323a","tid":644144,"uid":76632,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"職場三寶<br />\n<br />\n唔知，唔識，唔理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:04:35.000Z","msg":